{"tid":626520,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中共推遲與西方磋商　劉霞獲釋無期","createTime":"2018-04-12T07:42:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-12T08:09:23.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9139c36d4a86cd196f40d8ab33e3a0ebade00c2a","tid":626520,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T07:42:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180412/20358933\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180412%2F20358933&d=nFNULF6bYlw0oEjJ%2BVHHJW6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=6eea43a2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180412%2F20358933&h=f60b87f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180412/20358933</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中共推遲與西方磋商　劉霞獲釋無期<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180412/large/1523463081_1231.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180412%2Flarge%2F1523463081_1231.jpg&h=74ed7158&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n已故諾貝爾和平獎得主劉曉波的遺孀劉霞（圖），受到北京當局長期無理軟禁，身心飽受煎熬。有知情人士表示，對於釋放劉霞，中國使出「拖」字訣，多次推遲和西方各國磋商討論，外界越來越擔心，劉霞未必能在近期獲釋。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n要劉暉做人質　劉霞卻步<br />\n<br />\n對於營救劉霞，西方國家一直小心謹慎，希望爭取北京早日放人。然而，中國卻一直打「兩會牌」，以全國人民代表大會、全國政協會議為由，拖延討論劉霞問題。兩會上月結束，當局仍未放人；外界越來越擔心，劉霞未必能在近期獲釋。<br />\n<br />\n劉霞的朋友野渡指出，中國政府擔心劉霞移居西方後，將會大爆北京的黑幕，令北京當局相當尷尬，於是拖得就拖。野渡指出，北京亦看中劉霞的弱點，就是劉霞和弟弟劉暉的緊密關係。野渡指出，北京當局可能跟劉霞說，你可以走，不過劉暉要留下來做「人質」，令劉霞卻步。<br />\n<br />\n人權組織「人權監察」中國總監理察森認為，西方國家和國際組織未能通力合作，無法在外製造巨大輿論壓力，令北京不得不放劉霞，是劉霞遲遲未能重獲自由的原因之一。<br />\n<br />\n路透社  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n遭「劉霞式」軟禁　50人堵家門　王全璋妻露台抗爭　斥國保走狗<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n84歲異見教授遭迫害　降職減薪"},{"pid":"18d352903a07e52214ac03165b5c3cde61c634a6","tid":626520,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T08:09:23.000Z","msg":"硬膠泛民打手LIKLN<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/09/191003_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F09%2F191003_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=3124d977&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/09/191008_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F09%2F191008_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=ff15f2d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/10/201929_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F10%2F201929_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=27225035&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}